Sure, here are some example sentences that use the word "jug" in different forms and positions:

1. *Jug* Srbije je poznat po svojim vinogradima. (*South* Serbia is known for its vineyards.) 
2. Ljeto je, pa je vreme da se okupamo u *jugu*. (It's summer, so it's time to swim in the *south*.)
3. Planiramo da idemo na odmor na *jug*. (We're planning to go on vacation *south*.)
4. *Jug*ozapadni vjetar nam donosi kišu. (*South*westerly wind brings us rain.)
5. Kupio sam novi set čaša sa motivima *juga*. (I bought a new set of glasses with *southern* motifs.)
6. *Jug*oistočna Azija ima bogatu kulturu i istoriju. (*Southeast* Asia has a rich culture and history.)
7. Danas je južni *jug* u Srbiji jako topao. (Today, the southern *region* in Serbia is very hot.)
8. Posadio sam nekoliko biljaka u *južnom* dijelu vrta. (I planted a few plants in the *southern* part of the garden.)

I hope these examples help!